lead_paragraph: Two Manchester United fans hid inside an Old Trafford toilet and spent Friday night inside the stadium in the hope of watching their team play Arsenal in the Premier League on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Two Fans Spent Night Inside Old Trafford Ahead of Arsenal Game
